snippet.title: Action Hollywood (Arcade) 1995 Longplay
snippet.description: A slightly more modern game this time with Action Hollywood from 1995. In the same style as Jumpin' Jackson or Q'Bert, the goal is to turn all tiles over in order to complete the level. This game has many hidden points to gain across its levels, which you can choose to do in any order.
